FBIS3-60845 "jptot001__l94093" JPRS-TOT-94-001-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 7 January 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA RUSSIA Four Caucasians Kidnap Children; No Motive Given Helicopter Lands in Krasnodar; Talks Continue LD2312184993 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1830 GMT 23 Dec 93 LD2312184993 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Krasnodar, 23 Dec (ITAR-TASS) -- The helicopter with the terrorists and their hostages has just landed in one of the military airfields near Krasnodar. Talks immediately began between representatives of law enforcement bodies and the terrorists. They still demand an airplane to fly across the Russian border. In the opinion of specialists, the helicopter will not be able to continue its flight today -- it's already nightfall.
